caption.p: Chromatogram obtained by HPLC/APCI-MS/MS in positive mode from the carotenoid standards mixture. 1 = trans-fucoxanthin (50 ppm/); 2 = trans-astaxanthin (100 ppm); 3 = trans-lutein (100 ppm); IS = internal standard (86 ppm); 4 = trans-canthaxanthin (40 ppm); 5 = trans-cryptoxanthin (100 ppm); 6 = trans-α-carotene (100 ppm); 7 = trans-β-carotene (120 ppm).
